{"tid":818733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清潔工裸體商機！　辣媽「性感脫衣打掃","createTime":"2018-09-14T09:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T12:44:17.000Z","uid":179810,"like":666,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"785a1235623f864d02bceb45f4c2da6436f7e98f","tid":818733,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"澳洲昆士蘭（Queensland）一間清潔公司推出「裸體」服務，客戶可以選擇要男性還是女性清潔工，同時還能選擇清潔工要穿著近乎裸體的衣物或是直接裸體來打掃，引發當地議員抨擊，不過該公司表示他們的業務需求蒸蒸日上，該公司一名女員工更透露，自己透過該工作每年賺進10.4萬美元，而且每周只要工作16小時。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/13/1542182-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F1542182-XXL.jpg&h=1b176328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲清潔公司推出裸體清潔服務。（圖／翻攝自Bare All Cleaning Service）<br />\n<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，清潔公司「Bare All Cleaning Service」約成立5個月，該公司在官網上表示，他們提供家居清潔、清洗窗戶等各種不同服務，同時客戶可以選擇要男生或女生，還可以決定清潔工要穿著比基尼、濕T恤、裸上身或是全裸，不同的服裝、服務報價都不同。該公司指出，他們的服務讓無聊的苦差事變得有趣、性感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/13/1542165-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F1542165-XXL.jpg&h=95698617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲清潔公司推出裸體清潔服務。（圖／翻攝自Bare All Cleaning Service）<br />\n<br />\n一名在該公司擔任清潔工的28歲的單親辣媽透露，自己是商學畢業生，曾做過普通的清潔工作，但在該公司工作能賺到雙倍的薪水，工作時間也減少一半，現在她每週只要工作16小時，但是年收入卻達到10.4萬美元，她說：「我有一個很棒的身體，所以為什麼不炫耀它呢？我喜歡裸體而且享受肌膚在清掃時的感覺，所以我非常喜歡這份工作！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/13/1542166-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F1542166-XXL.jpg&h=e2f754e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲清潔公司推出裸體清潔服務。（圖／翻攝自Bare All Cleaning Service）<br />\n<br />\n不過該公司的服務也引起當地市議員抨擊，市議員克里克洛（Dawn Crichlow）7月時就表示，昆士蘭州連裸體海灘都沒有合法了，該公司怎麼會合法呢？克里克洛更質疑，這些員工用當裸體清潔工來過生活，但當地並不需要這種可恥的服務，要他們「去找一份真正的工作！」<br />\n<br />\n對此該公司創辦人瓊斯（Brett Jones）則表示，該公司提供的不是性服務，而是清潔服務，不同之處在於人們得到的報酬比平常要多很多，稱他們的服務讓清潔工作不再乏味，更強調克里克洛的評論是「重傷」公司員工，堅稱該公司的服務完全合法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/a/a0/Fuxxgood_MA.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20101021052843\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fa%2Fa0%2FFuxxgood_MA.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20101021052843&h=abe93eac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54eeef826ab3b0fd08e631487d76c2805021c0c5","tid":818733,"uid":67500,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"鬼婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb2ea9e11439453dde48bad993ef7a8f359a57c","tid":818733,"uid":57633,"like":571,"dislike":4,"score":567,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:56:17.000Z","msg":"又一次證明av走得好前"},{"pid":"16a3d0000891a9862f448a79229d4f6c09afe576","tid":818733,"uid":30309,"like":217,"dislike":1,"score":216,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"16小時一週<br />\n104k usd一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf69ecf803a7966d64b074ddc649adf8579dc97f","tid":818733,"uid":59898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f8af2ab1c413106579cbb8ef40cb725dbfc326","tid":818733,"uid":41368,"like":264,"dislike":6,"score":258,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:04:36.000Z","msg":"打掃完又可以me too告9條友賺返筆"},{"pid":"ae5c8b4637b1ad9592c60a88afc591827115cacd","tid":818733,"uid":41368,"like":215,"dislike":1,"score":214,"quote":{"pid":"16a3d0000891a9862f448a79229d4f6c09afe576","tid":818733,"uid":30309,"like":217,"dislike":1,"score":216,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"16小時一週<br />\n104k usd一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:05:46.000Z"